# Shopify checkout passthrough — mapleterroir.com is now Cloudflare Pages,
# so /cart/* and /checkout/* paths must redirect to the Shopify storefront
# domain. Without this, every Shopify-issued checkout URL 404s. The 302! is
# Cloudflare Pages' force-redirect even if a static file matches.
/cart/*       https://maple-terroir.myshopify.com/cart/:splat       302!
/checkout/*   https://maple-terroir.myshopify.com/checkout/:splat   302!
/checkouts/*  https://maple-terroir.myshopify.com/checkouts/:splat  302!
/account      https://maple-terroir.myshopify.com/account           302!
/account/*    https://maple-terroir.myshopify.com/account/:splat    302!

